<br>
To stay balanced you really have to measure damage per hour and not just DPS. DPS does not list how long a paladin/mage has to sit to regen mana. <br>
<br>
Should the mage pet deal more damage than a paladin and in addition be full health/mana faster than the paladin then I would be strongly against the mage pet dealing more damage than a paladin for obvious reasons. <br>
<br>
Real balancing should be based on contributions over an hour not during a battle. <p>Senchy Solariatus60 Crusader of Rodcet Nife
